                        "content": "A client is admitted with an exacerbation of multiple sclerosis. The nurse is assessing the client for possible precipitating risk factors. Which factor, if reported by the client, would the nurse identify as being unrelated to the exacerbation?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nThe onset or exacerbation of multiple sclerosis can be preceded by a number of different factors, including physical stress (e.g., vaccination, excessive exercise), emotional stress, fatigue, infection, physical injury, pregnancy, extremes in environmental temperature, and high humidity. No methods of primary prevention are known. Intake of fruits and vegetables is a healthy and an unrelated item.",
                        "id": "b51281c40b14417da1b59105b52f4072",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "00f0bf1b73b74b6585adecf501b24562",
                                "content": "Observe the client demonstrating the transfer technique."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5a540ab970fc4cdca5780a0637746e61",
                                "content": "Start a restorative nursing program before an injury occurs."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "65ff8f858ce74232b52d1804dc45c82c",
                                "content": "Seize the opportunity to discuss potential nursing home placement."
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "5d43197fe50f4bb19976185dc3180bcf",
                                "content": "Determine the number of falls that the client has had in recent weeks."
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
